s3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them eternal life on condition of fidelity </div><div class="t ma98 x58 h4 y156d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to God&apos;s law. Thus the patriarchs received </div><div class="t m204d xaf h2f y12e3 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">33 2 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
